Job Description

  To Supervise ,co-ordinate and deploy site foreman, subcontractor and supplier effectively to ensure that the project is completed according to specifications, quality standards, cost and time frame
  Attend meetings and negotiation with clients, subcontractors and suppliers
  Resolve site problem by investing the problems, develop solution, make recommendation to management
  Ensure compliance with all legal requirements concerning safety, supervision and quality control
  Ensure customer service satisfaction and maintain good client relationships
  And any other tasks or assignments as may be assigned by the employer from time to time

Requirements&nbsp;

  Candidate must have at least 3 years of experience in similar electrical works.
  Good understanding of Singapore Code of practice for electrical
  Possess good communication, leadership and interpersonal skill.
  Hardworking and possess positive attitude.
